<p>A dropmarker is a button with an arrow which will reveal more details when pressed. A dropmarker is not intended to be used as a separate element, but as part of another element. For instance the <span class="script">template.XULElem("menulist")</span> and the popup type of <span class="script">template.XULElem("datepicker")</span> use a dropmarker, that when pressed, will reveal a popup menu.</p>
